{
  "productName": "LocalBeat",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "identifier": "com.theartmedium.localbeat",
  "build": {
    "frontendDist": "../src"
  },
  "app": {
    "windows": [{
      "title": "LocalBeat",
      "width": 900,
      "height": 640,
      "minWidth": 640,
      "minHeight": 480,
      "resizable": true,
      "fullscreen": false
    }],
    "security": {
      "csp": null
    }
  },
  "bundle": {
    "active": true,
    "icon": [
      "icons/32x32.png",
      "icons/128x128.png",
      "icons/icon.icns",
      "icons/icon.ico"
    ]
  }
}
Steps:
Open LocalBeat/src-tauri/tauri.conf.json on GitHub
Click ✏️ edit
Ctrl+A → delete all
Paste the above
Commit to main and re-run the workflow 🚀